```shallot/shallot_website/src/retro_hero.rs
//! Retro Hero Section ‚Äî "Act 1: The 90s Web / Act 2: The Punchline"
//!
//! A lovingly accurate recreation of the 1998 Geocities/Netscape era,
//! built entirely in pure Rust + CSS. No JavaScript. No framer-motion.
//! CSS Scroll-Driven Animations replace the React/framer punchline reveal.
//!
//! Structure:
//!   1. The "90s Webpage" ‚Äî authentically terrible, deliberately so
//!   2. The Punchline ‚Äî "‚òùÔ∏è No JavaScript doesn't have to look like this."
//!   3. The Arrow ‚Äî bouncing CSS emoji pointing to the modern showcase below

use maud::{html, Markup, PreEscaped};

